title: Master Yi left the blue side fountain with 856 move speed
body: at 7:30 in the morning. Rammus left the red side fountain with 2092 move speed, after ghosting, using Q and homeguards. Master Yi had homeguards and ult. If Rammus left red side 15 seconds later, how long will it take for Master Yi to kill himself on Rammus's W and Thornmail?
